aedit - 2.0.0
* Added support for regions and regions FX
* Added html export
* html default format for report
* Added "-text" option, for plain text report
* Added "-verbose" option for visualization and text report
* Added class mdict. Internally used for storing tracks, plugins, regions and regions FX
* Menu options for changing "verbosity" and "html/text" format
* Some refactoring


aedit - 1.0.0
* first public release


